[EXCERPT:PhysicsBlend]

This value controls the blend between an animation that is playing, and the Physics Asset Tool's physical simulation. Values greater than 0.0 will have some amount of physics applied to them, while a value of 1.0 means the skeletal mesh is completely controlled by the Physics Asset.

[VAR:ToolTipFullLink]
Engine/Physics/PhysicsAssetEditor/Properties#physicsassettoolproperties
[/VAR]

[/EXCERPT:PhysicsBlend]




